# 🛍️ Retail Sales Analysis

This notebook-driven case study explores a fictional clothing retailer's transactional dataset to uncover insights about product sales, store performance, and shipping behavior.

## 📊 Key Objectives

- Analyze transactional volume by store and product category
- Track revenue trends over time
- Assess the impact of shipping methods on delivery outcomes
- Recommend strategies to optimize product mix and logistics

## 📁 Files Included

- `C2 - Case Study - Python Fundamentals - Complete.ipynb` – the main analysis notebook
- `Products.csv`, `Stores.csv`, `Transactions.csv`, `Shipping.csv` – supporting datasets

## 🧠 Skills Demonstrated

- Data cleaning and transformation with pandas
- Exploratory data analysis and visualizations
- Business performance interpretation
- Insight storytelling in notebook format

